<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">System</div>
    <h2>How the System Works</h2>

<pre>tokens.ts ──→ tokens.css ──→ brand/dist/tokens.css
     │                                │
     ▼                                ▼
templates/*.html  ──→  pdf.ts/image.ts  ──→  PDFs / PNGs
     │
     ▼
site/*.njk  ──→  11ty  ──→  brand/dist/site/  ──→  website /brand/  (via git submodule)</pre>

    <h3>Generators</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Script</th><th>Command</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>build:tokens</code></td><td><code>tsx scripts/build-tokens.ts</code></td><td>Regenerate tokens.css + tokens.json from tokens.ts</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>build:dist</code></td><td><code>bash scripts/build-dist.sh</code></td><td>Build the full Brand Distribution (site + assets + fonts + tokens.css)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>dev</code></td><td><code>11ty --serve</code></td><td>Serve the Brand Site at localhost:3000/brand/ with live reload</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pdf</code></td><td><code>tsx generators/pdf.ts</code></td><td>Markdown → branded A4 PDF</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>image</code></td><td><code>tsx generators/image.ts</code></td><td>HTML/SVG → PNG (banners, social)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>export</code></td><td><code>tsx scripts/export-assets.ts</code></td><td>Regenerate all raster assets + document previews</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>build:skill</code></td><td><code>bash scripts/build-skill.sh</code></td><td>Package brand-engine.skill</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Token Update Workflow</h3>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <p>Edit <code>brand/tokens.ts</code> — Change colors, fonts, or spacing values</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <p>Run <code>npm run dev</code> in <code>brand/</code> — Brand Site at localhost:3000/brand/ updates live as you tweak tokens</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <p>Commit and push the brand repo — that becomes the new "release" the website can consume</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <p>In the website repo: <code>git submodule update --remote _brand</code> → commit the new pin → deploy. The live <code>/brand/</code> page now reflects the new tokens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <h3>Skill Packaging</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-body); margin-top: 8px;">The brand system can be packaged as a Claude Code skill for agent use.</p>

<pre><code>npm run build:skill
# Output: dist/brand-engine.skill</code></pre>
  </div>
</section>

